[15.634792, "o", "\u001b[33mcommit 650dba427e0a9dcd118f41a4c5e35c8017550a5a\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\nAuthor: Test User <test@example.com>\u001b[m\r\nDate:   Sat Sep 13 17:54:33 2025 +0000\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n    Move to Stanford\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mdiff --git a/_includes/about.md b/_includes/about.md\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mindex 5322c14..7561d9e 100644\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1m--- a/_includes/about.md\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1m+++ b/_includes/about.md\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[36m@@ -1,3 +1,3 @@\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[31m-I am a sixth year PhD student at the [Paul G. Allen School of Computer Science & Engineering](https://www.cs.washington.edu/) at The University of Washington, \u001b[m \b\u001b[31mwhere I am advised by [Tim Althoff](http://www.timalthoff.com/). I am affiliated with [UW NLP](https://twitter.com/uwnlp).\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[32m+\u001b[m\u001b[32mI am a Postdoctoral Researcher at Stanford CS.\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n \u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[31m-**I am looking for a full time job!** If you think we would be a good match, please reach out. Previously, I was a Student Researcher at [Google Research](http\u001b[m \b\u001b[31ms://research.google/), an ML Research Intern at [Apple Health AI](https://machinele"]
[15.635021, "o", "arning.apple.com/work-with-us) and a data scientist and the second full-time \u001b[m \b\u001b[31memployee at [HealthRhythms](https://www.healthrhythms.com). \u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\\ No newline at end of file\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[32m+\u001b[m\u001b[32mPreviously, I was a Student Researcher at [Google Research](https://research.google/), an ML Research Intern at [Apple Health AI](https://machinelearning.apple\u001b[m \b\u001b[32m\u001b[m\u001b[32m.com/work-with-us) and a data scientist and the second full-time employee at [HealthRhythms](https://www.healthrhythms.com).\u001b[m\u001b[41m \u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\\ No newline at end of file\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mdiff --git a/_layouts/default.html b/_layouts/default.html\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mindex 3fe07ee..cff5b5e 100644\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1m--- a/_layouts/default.html\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1m+++ b/_layouts/default.html\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[36m@@ -27,7 +27,9 @@\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n     <link href=\"css/bootstrap.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n     <link href=\"css/style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n \u001b[m\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[31m-    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Noto+Sans+HK:100,300|Barlow+Condensed|PT+Mono|PT+Serif&"]
